A customer is considering BladeCenter H and S chassis. Which of the following is a reason
to implement BladeCenter H?
A. Support for 10Gb internal network
B. Support for SSD
C. Support for integrated disk drives
D. Support for 8Gb FC Switch Modules?
Answer: A
A customer has the following equipment installed in their data center:
-- an IBM BladeCenter H chassis
-- two power supplies
-- six HS22V blades
-- three Nortel 1/10 GB ESMs
The retail customer purchased a new HX5 with MAX5. Which of the following must be
added to install the HX5 with MAX5?
A. Two additional power supplies
B. Fibre Channel (FC) switches and SAN storage
C. A Nortel 1/10 GB ESM
D. SSD for the HX5
Answer: A

through a web interface from multiple remote locations. Which of the following questions
will provide the information necessary to design the best performing storage solution?
